27:56.093 --> 27:58.971
<i>Today, the victim is a pro-life</i>
<i>patriot... Well, who's next?</i>

27:59.137 --> 28:03.475
<i>Pregnant women recognizing the sanctity</i>
<i>of life growing inside of them?</i>

28:03.642 --> 28:05.936
