<i>by the Woke Warriors</i>

28:06.103 --> 28:08.647
<i>is on Senator Herbert Jackson's hands.</i>

28:10.691 --> 28:13.694
<i>We will provide updates</i>
<i>on this story as it develops.</i>

28:13.861 --> 28:17.197
<i>This is Beverly Hope.</i>
<i>Back to you in the studio.</i>

28:17.364 --> 28:19.074
CAMERAMAN: <i>And we're clear.</i>

28:19.241 --> 28:21.034
