31:35.479 --> 31:37.689
(EXHALES SHARPLY)

31:41.985 --> 31:43.570
(QUIETLY) Ah, fuck.

31:46.448 --> 31:48.492
It's the little things.
The tiny details.

31:48.575 --> 31:50.494
